{"word":"Zedekiah","slug":"zedekiah","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>Zedekiah</b> <a href=\"#/H6667\">H6667</a> <br/> 1. King of Judah:<br/> - Made king of Judah by Nebuchadnezzar<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=12&chapter=24&verse=18'>2Ki 24:18</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=3&verse=15'>1Ch 3:15</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=14&chapter=36&verse=10'>2Ch 36:10</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=24&chapter=37&verse=1'>Jer 37:1</a> <br/> - Throws off his allegiance to Nebuchadnezzar<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=12&chapter=24&verse=20'>2Ki 24:20</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=14&chapter=36&verse=13'>2Ch 36:13</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=24&chapter=52&verse=3'>Jer 52:3</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=26&chapter=17&verse=21'>Eze 17:21</a> <br/> - Forms an alliance with the king of Egypt<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=26&chapter=17&verse=18'>Eze 17:18</a> <br/> - The allegiance denounced:<br/> b by Jeremiah<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=14&chapter=36&verse=12'>2Ch 36:12</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=24&chapter=21&verse=14'>Jer 21:14</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=24&chapter=24&verse=10'>Jer 24:10</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=24&chapter=27&verse=22'>Jer 27:22</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=24&chapter=32&verse=5'>Jer 32:5</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=24&chapter=34'>Jer 34</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=24&chapter=37&verse=10'>Jer 37:10</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=24&chapter=37&verse=17'>Jer 37:17</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=24&chapter=38&verse=28'>Jer 38:28</a><br/> b by Ezekiel<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=26&chapter=12&verse=16'>Eze 12:16</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=26&chapter=17&verse=21'>Eze 17:21</a><br/> - Imprisons Jeremiah on account of his denunciations<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=24&chapter=32&verse=3'>Jer 32:3</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=24&chapter=37&verse=21'>Jer 37:21</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=24&chapter=38&verse=28'>Jer 38:28</a> <br/> - Seeks the intercession of Jeremiah with God in his behalf<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=24&chapter=21&verse=3'>Jer 21:3</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=24&chapter=37&verse=3'>Jer 37:3</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=24&chapter=38&verse=27'>Jer 38:27</a> <br/> - Wicked reign of<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=12&chapter=24&verse=20'>2Ki 24:20</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=14&chapter=36&verse=13'>2Ch 36:13</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=24&chapter=37&verse=2'>Jer 37:2</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=24&chapter=38&verse=5'>Jer 38:5</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=24&chapter=38&verse=19'>Jer 38:19</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=24&chapter=38&verse=26'>Jer 38:26</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=24&chapter=52&verse=2'>Jer 52:2</a> <br/> - Nebuchadnezzar destroys the city and temple, takes him captive to Babylon, blinds his eyes, slays his sons<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=12&chapter=25&verse=10'>2Ki 25:10</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=14&chapter=36&verse=20'>2Ch 36:20</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=24&chapter=1&verse=3'>Jer 1:3</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=24&chapter=32&verse=2'>Jer 32:2</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=24&chapter=39&verse=10'>Jer 39:10</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=24&chapter=51&verse=59'>Jer 51:59</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=24&chapter=52&verse=30'>Jer 52:30</a> <br/> 2. Grandson of Jehoiakim<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=3&verse=16'>1Ch 3:16</a><br/> 3. A false prophet<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=24&chapter=29&verse=23'>Jer 29:23</a><br/> 4. A prince of Judah<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=24&chapter=36&verse=12'>Jer 36:12</a><br/> 5. A false prophet:<br/> - Prophesies to Ahab victory over the Syrians, instead of defeat<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=22&verse=11'>1Ki 22:11</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=14&chapter=18&verse=10'>2Ch 18:10</a> <br/> - Smites Micaiah, the true prophet<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=22&verse=24'>1Ki 22:24</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=14&chapter=18&verse=23'>2Ch 18:23</a> "}]}